《'''消失的影像'''》({{lang-fr|'''L'image manquante'''}})，又译作《'''残缺影像'''》 ，是一部2013年[[潘礼德|潘礼德]]执导、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]与[[法国|法国]]合拍的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/the-missing-picture-review-1200490158/|title=Cannes Film Review: ‘The Missing Picture’|publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''|date=2013-05-30|accessdate=2014-02-24|archive-date=2014-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226010329/http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/the-missing-picture-review-1200490158/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、内容有关[[红色高棉|红色高棉]]的[[纪录片|纪录片]]<ref name="HWR">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/missing-picture-limage-manquante-cannes-525380|title=The Missing Picture (L'Image manquante): Cannes Review|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|work=Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109185031/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/missing-picture-limage-manquante-cannes-525380|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片的一半内容由[[新闻|新闻]]与纪实片段组成，剩下的由[[泥偶|泥偶]]代替人物表演<ref name="BBCMissing"></ref>。

本片入选[[第66届坎城影展|第66届坎城影展]]的[[一種注目|一種注目]]/Un certain regard单元<ref name="Cannes2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|title=2013 Official Selection|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|work=Cannes|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211120304/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，获得高度好评<ref name="HWR-UCR">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|title=Cannes: 'The Missing Picture' Wins Un Certain Regard Prize|date=26 May 2013|accessdate=26 May 2013|work=Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528150056/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|dead-url=no}}</ref>；并在同年的[[马尼拉国际电影节|马尼拉国际电影节]]上赢得评审团大奖<ref name="PDI">{{cite web |url=http://entertainment.inquirer.net/126507/cinemanila-2013-winners-awarded-saturday-night |title=Cinemanila 2013 winners awarded Saturday night |accessdate=2013-12-28 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |archive-date=2015-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119204319/http://entertainment.inquirer.net/126507/cinemanila-2013-winners-awarded-saturday-night |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

